{"entity":{"id":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","type":"chapter","slug":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","label":"Ps.114","rawId":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","book":{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","slug":"ps","label":"Psalms","subtitle":"Poetry-Wisdom","count":2461,"description":"150 chapters, 1026 people, 118 places"}},"stats":{"verses":8,"people":2,"places":2,"events":0},"nodes":[{"id":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Ps.114","slug":"ps_114","score":8},{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Psalms","slug":"ps","score":2461},{"id":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Jacob (Israel)","slug":"israel_682","score":2},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":1},{"id":"rec5dSSsOutWlH2fW","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Jordan","slug":"jordan_653","score":2},{"id":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Egypt","slug":"egypt_362","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","target":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","label":"part of"},{"source":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","target":"rec5dSSsOutWlH2fW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUja3OLY83mrWKE","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec87lPt29pTRfWvb","ref":"Ps.114.1","text":"When Israel went out of Egypt, the house of Jacob from a people of strange language;"},{"id":"recLrgo4f8fbLuDMK","ref":"Ps.114.2","text":"Judah was his sanctuary, and Israel his dominion."},{"id":"recMHQHDVcm0CpUq6","ref":"Ps.114.3","text":"The sea saw it, and fled: Jordan was driven back."},{"id":"recS8pXSH1ZmIxKm1","ref":"Ps.114.4","text":"The mountains skipped like rams, and the little hills like lambs."},{"id":"recPC5Ac90lVunugA","ref":"Ps.114.5","text":"What ailed thee, O thou sea, that thou fleddest? thou Jordan, that thou wast driven back?"},{"id":"reczIRxHShhTXioA7","ref":"Ps.114.6","text":"Ye mountains, that ye skipped like rams; and ye little hills, like lambs?"},{"id":"recnyi0VqW5oRN3Cr","ref":"Ps.114.7","text":"Tremble, thou earth, at the presence of the Lord, at the presence of the God of Jacob;"},{"id":"rec5lswMEA6i858r4","ref":"Ps.114.8","text":"Which turned the rock into a standing water, the flint into a fountain of waters."}]}
